_aChangeLog.text: Added unpack sprite and audio file

_sText:
"Misplaced nautical charts, trade winds, shortwave miscommunication, midnight whispers, amorxxx"

The first act in the Tradewinds KZ map series - a medium-length, intermediate difficulty climb experience set in an expansive arctic facility in the tundra.
Thanks to Lil Can and Squidski for helping with a major bug during the map's development, and to Smaed for general technical help and playtesting.

Act 2 coming soon.
